      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Conferences\" title=\"Conferences\">Conferences</a> * Advances in Computer Games 13</b>\n</p><p><b><a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_12\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 12\">&lt; Prev</a> <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_14\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 14\">Next &gt;</a></b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:TheRedBrick2.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d3/TheRedBrick2.JPG/300px-TheRedBrick2.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"224\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/d/d3/TheRedBrick2.JPG 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:TheRedBrick2.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The Red Brick, <a href=\"/Tilburg_University\" title=\"Tilburg University\">Tilburg University</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Advances in Computer Games 13</b>,<br />\nfrom  November 20 to 22, <a href=\"/Timeline#2011\" title=\"Timeline\">2011</a>, <a href=\"/Tilburg_University\" title=\"Tilburg University\">Tilburg University</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tilburg\">Tilburg</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Netherlands\">The Netherlands</a>. In conjunction with the <a href=\"/16th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"16th Computer Olympiad\">16th Computer Olympiad</a>, the <a href=\"/WCCC_2011\" title=\"WCCC 2011\">WCCC 2011</a>, and the <a href=\"/WCSC_2011\" title=\"WCSC 2011\">WCSC 2011</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Proceedings\